 Analysis, and Communication Studies, among others.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aBusinessxLanguage. 0aEconomicsxLanguage. 0aFigures of speech. 0aInterdisciplinary approach to knowledge. 0aMetaphor. 4aKognitive Linguistik. 4aMetaphern. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aApplied Linguistics.  aCognitive Linguistics.  aMetaphor and Economics.1 aBlazkova, Hana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaller, Paloma Tejada, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCamiciottoli, Belinda Crawford, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChung, Siaw-Fong, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEubanks, Philip, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFuertes-Olivera, Pedro A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGuerra, Antonio Guzmán, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHerrera-Soler, Honesto, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHerrera-Soler, Honesto, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHolmgreen, Lise-Lotte, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLittlemore, Jeannette, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMouton, Nicolaas T.O., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aResche, Catherine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSardinha, Tony Berber, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSkorczynska, Hanna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVelasco-Sacristán, Marisol, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWhi